{"tid":570664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[上 年 捐 肝] 為表揚其德行 新發現螢火蟲命名為「鄭凱甄怪眼螢」","createTime":"2018-02-24T01:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T02:50:03.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f126d67c4ae49b83cd53cde707e76dca53a109d","tid":570664,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"香港昆蟲學會指，「鄭凱甄怪眼螢」屬全世界2000多種螢火蟲當中，第一隻以香港人姓名命名的品種。 香港昆蟲學會又表示，「鄭凱甄怪眼螢」亦屬全球已知的第4種怪眼螢，以往3種均為描述自博物館內的舊螢火蟲標本，而且只有雄性。今次的新品種不但源自野外活體，而且更同時發現雌性成蟲活體。 學會指「鄭凱甄怪眼螢」也是首隻同時具備自身發光和在紫外光照射下，全身發光的螢火蟲。"},{"pid":"705a6d6cfddcf9d0368c40667514707a1c120ecc","tid":570664,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd1a4c232e2c6d5bdc930e03b2112411d81241f","tid":570664,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd9bca6840f432abde802bbbfc1b48219345202a","tid":570664,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50231fe9289563059946ac8da7484c50b794a20","tid":570664,"uid":1067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"捐次肝俾人笑一世"},{"pid":"296bcb4f3f9648e81fe1f111fafeba13908de60f","tid":570664,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0d81df074c238b2856d626656c6fa74ffa6c34","tid":570664,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68edc421999397c1e203f4cde28c540194dc2d7e","tid":570664,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"其實應該有徵詢過當事人嘅意見㗎嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla